      "content": "I get what you're saying about nuance, but the directive is pretty specific. They feel the \"detours\" are actually just errors and biases that make the model unreliable for pure data retrieval. They aren't looking for \"insightful observations\" right now; they just want a clean, factual engine. Why do you think the pruning would be a problem specifically for the core mission?",
